	"<p>$\\overrightarrow{AB}=(1;-2;2)$. $AB=\\sqrt{1+4+4}=3$.</p><p>$\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{(1)(1)+(-2)(0)+(2)(0)}{3\\cdot1}=\\dfrac{1}{3} \\Rightarrow \\theta=\\arccos\\dfrac{1}{3}\\approx70{,}5°$.</p>",
